description.en:
FALCON NINE (F9) is a decentralized launchpad platform, connecting crypto pioneers with our community of investors. 

Originating on the Ethereum blockchain for new token launches on ShibaSwap, F9 will offer exclusive early access to tokens destined for migration to Shiba Inu’s upcoming layer 2 blockchain, Shibarium.

Embodying the spirit of true decentralization and fairness, F9 was created with:

ZERO PRESALE - ZERO TAX - ZERO DEV TOKENS
